$$f(x) = |x - 2|$$<br><br>$$ \therefore $$ $$f(f(x)) = \left| {|x - 2| - 2} \right| = g(x)$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow g(x) = \left| {|x - 2| - 2} \right| = \left\{ {\matrix{
